4i-Giao/T%E1%BA%B7ng-t%E1%BB%B3/poem-0FyTzLTQOKw7KF86V58RFQ">Tặng tỳ - 贈婢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Giao/author-DvHfHBMTOurAHhw0My6rxQ">Thôi Giao</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-m%E1%BA%A1n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-pfuUA7uGS4qURp0ZBic0fA">Tuyệt cú mạn hứng kỳ 5 - 絕句漫興其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Nguy%E1%BB%87t-Anh/T%E1%BB%B1-ho%C3%A0i/poem-0Dsu8m-n85dJPoSfWO_giw">Tự hoài - 敘懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Nguy%E1%BB%87t-Anh/author-Etl4IImmKFqErJL8B4U-xw">Từ Nguyệt Anh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%C3%A0m-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-Tam-L%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-phu-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-Xj0HyTmcYLTH5EbtPu2ptA">Tương Đàm điếu Tam Lư đại phu kỳ 1 - 湘潭弔三閭大夫其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br></div>	</div>
